{%- comment -%}
  Thin section wrapper around the kerastase-collection-extras snippet (FAQ + FAQPage JSON-LD +
  related-articles). For multi-section OS 2.0 collection templates (e.g. collection.krglossabsolu,
  collection.krpremiere), add this section to the END of the template's `order` so the metafield
  content renders at the bottom of the page — rather than editing a shared bespoke section.
  Guarded by the snippet, so it no-ops on collections without the contract metafields.
{%- endcomment -%}
{% render 'kerastase-collection-extras' %}
{% schema %}
{ "name": "Kérastase extras", "tag": "section", "settings": [] }
{% endschema %}
